Package org.eclipse.m2m.atl.emftvm.jit

Class JITCodeBlock

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.m2m.atl.emftvm.jit.JITCodeBlock
public abstract class JITCodeBlock extends Object
Interface for code generated by the JITCodeBlock compiler.
